{
  "stem": "20800.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he come to this, and asks, what is that?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We said, this is our things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, go [POINTS] further up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We want to see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we started to open these-- our things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we wouldn't live long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And back there starting shooting and screaming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this chap that had us under a gun, ran down there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we saw he ran, we start to run.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We left everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We went in the little thing, whatever we had on us, we run.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And likely he never come back after us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We left these whole things, the suitcase and whatever we had, and ran away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "From now on, we were really on the run, run, and run, and run.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We come [SIGHS] to a place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We was asking for piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we helped the Cossacks to do some cutting grass.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Some-- there was a lot of sunflowers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we-- we cut the sunflowers, and then we we did get some of sunflower seeds.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was our meal for the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we didn't stop in one particular-- we were-- wherever we stopped to get something to eat, we work for it to get something to eat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And till we come to another [NON-ENGLISH], Nikolaevka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And what happened, while we were working we saw a shed, practically a shed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we said, look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We stay here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We come there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was empty, nobody around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So me, my sister, and my mother, we went inside and stayed inside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And from there on, I said, my mother to stay there, not to go nowhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because we were frightened any time Germans will come, and my sister, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But I was going to look for something to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
